ched into position.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her block\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"breaths\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"position\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was in the lead by 25 metres of the first stroke, the butterfly, and turned into the backstroke with a 1.35sec lead over American 18-year-old, Katie Grimes.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Grimes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Grimes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Grimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"25 metres\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"the first stroke\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"the butterfly\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the backstroke\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"a 1.35sec lead\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That lead was 1.56sec when they started the breaststroke, and a couple of years ago that might have been an opportunity for her rivals.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That lead\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaststroke\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"her rivals\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But McIntosh has turned her weakness into a strength, and she raced away from the field.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4402671886890273e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her weakness\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"a strength\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh has hardly been hiding.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4402671886890273e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the world record holder and this is, remarkably, her secondOlympicsafter she appeared in Tokyo aged 14 and set a national record in the 400m freestyle.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8752525026865434, \"rank\": 0.14252743712606503, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world record holder\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"a national record\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2785}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m freestyle\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the summer of 2022 she established herself as not just a bundle of potential but one of the best swimmers in the world, still only 15, with Commonwealth and World Championship gold medals in medley and butterfly.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2952, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.50462947252711e-19, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"not just a bundle\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"potential\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"the best swimmers\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"butterfly\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She soon moved from Canada to Florida to train with renowned coach Bret Arkey, and he structured her daily \\\"grind\\\", as she calls it.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9981782256173756, \"rank\": 0.0012228764646918704, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 3056, \"end\": 3063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"score\": 0.8105716585180887, \"rank\": 0.194593782909897, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\"}, {\"begin\": 3093, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bret_Hart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.532218098917392e-14, \"text\": \"Bret\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bret_Hart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bret_Hart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her daily \\\"grind\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of specialising at an early stage as most swimmers tend to do, Arkey and McIntosh worked hard on all four disciplines with particular attention to her supposed weakness, the breaststroke.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3240, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4402671886890273e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an early stage\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"most swimmers\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"Arkey\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"all four disciplines\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3284}, {\"ngram\": \"particular attention\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"her supposed weakness\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaststroke\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That versatility kept training more varied and interesting.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That versatility\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prodigious talent requires a blend of nature and nurture and McIntosh's mum, Jill Horstead, can take plenty of credit for both.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4402671886890273e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}, {\"begin\": 3493, \"end\": 3506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Horstead\", \"score\": 1.0, \